{"tid":1512370,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"葵盛東手足注意！","createTime":"2019-08-28T00:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T12:14:47.000Z","uid":264308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1d52cdb71125fef613450df12dc3cb998cde5b03","tid":1512370,"uid":264308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:47:44.000Z","msg":"小弟住葵盛東其中一楝嘅中層 我個層有個鄰居 識咗廿年 平時見面都會笑住打招呼 佢笑容係好和藹可親 比人感覺係好慈祥個啲 <br />\n<br />\n直到琴晚我落公園咆哮咁啱比佢見到 之後比佢捉住訓話 話我地嘈住人瞓覺 又爆自己係福建人 話中國點點點好 乜乜柒柒 我地後生一代比人洗咗腦 遊行企前線有$5000收<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後話自己會蒙面拎鐵通係後樓梯打啲咆哮嘅人 見到我都無情講咁話 （其實前一晚我真係起後樓梯咆哮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）又話夜晚會跟住啲單拖咆哮獸 去啲暗角位摙撚死佢 又叫我遊行唔好企咁前 當係識咗我咁耐又係鄰居先講咁多 佢仲要愈講愈嬲 嬲到個人震震地 又話如果有得買AK 自己一定會買枝掃低幾百個之後自己去坐監 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好彩後尾佢講講下講到話自己去過好多地方旅行 我即刻轉咗個話題追問佢覺得邊度旅行最好之類 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個時勁驚佢講講下會嬲到郁9我<br />\n<br />\n比佢訓話完 我照落去連儂牆原本約咗個friend 整野 但係一路整一路勁驚比佢見到 係咁叫我個friend睇水 <br />\n<br />\n如果各位葵盛東巴絲打夜晚整連儂牆或者咆哮真係要小心啲 切勿單拖 多個人多個照應<br />\n<br />\n但我之後都會照出 最多鄭家穎遊擊隊 等佢捉唔到我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2EqOUvi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2EqOUvi.jpg&h=56db7a08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2VnBiXa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2VnBiXa.jpg&h=0117afa4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b405a2d68e40db8b79dded5eaf0e87cc02cb027","tid":1512370,"uid":52817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:47:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NSAWdB2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNSAWdB2.jpg&h=7e1fa5a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8398ac30e7ab2ec3cc73622a15f7968a604402a7","tid":1512370,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:49:47.000Z","msg":"人地都出曬聲 仲唔買返袋20kg米？"},{"pid":"769c2b4c040b9e92046745bb6764028a6f8e3ec5","tid":1512370,"uid":288351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:51:55.000Z","msg":"咁你唔問佢點解會出現係香港"},{"pid":"b4da27bbf25340565b98a86cc6c96942d904cafd","tid":1512370,"uid":264308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"769c2b4c040b9e92046745bb6764028a6f8e3ec5","tid":1512370,"uid":288351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:51:55.000Z","msg":"咁你唔問佢點解會出現係香港"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:53:27.000Z","msg":"個陣真心淆 完全唔敢駁佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f9baf363d61580e3c637f6080e7ffb77a5426b","tid":1512370,"uid":288351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:54:29.000Z","msg":"諗定下次再遇到呢d人反駁佢地"},{"pid":"2e13c8ffc279fe8f137ba5a34dd00cb1f99b2ba9","tid":1512370,"uid":244034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4da27bbf25340565b98a86cc6c96942d904cafd","tid":1512370,"uid":264308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"769c2b4c040b9e92046745bb6764028a6f8e3ec5","tid":1512370,"uid":288351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:51:55.000Z","msg":"咁你唔問佢點解會出現係香港"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:53:27.000Z","msg":"個陣真心淆 完全唔敢駁佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:55:32.000Z","msg":"問左佢即係打你，呢D覺得自己處於下風同無面就打人"},{"pid":"38232b939bc50b68a5b134e20f7a3df2ab832a29","tid":1512370,"uid":62554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:59:38.000Z","msg":"呢啲人無得救<br />\n大叫支持解放軍入城攬炒囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c5baaf320c6da7f1ea1c7cfbeeeca36296fa673","tid":1512370,"uid":264308,"like":0,"d